author: Palatine

comments.content: The Headline is News Gothic Bold
I don't see any other fonts.

Nope, that's [Franklin Gothic Condensed](http://web.archive.org/web/20131106081600/http:/www.fontshop.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=catalog.fontdetail&displayfontid=LH.217.0.2&attributes.sampleSize=24&sampleText=Origin+Motorsport+The+new+911+GT3+RS&sampleSize=18). News Gothic has less contrast.
Damn. The second wrong ID. Not my day ;)

That's alright Schnappi, you got further than I did! Your effort is much appreciated.

Thanks Yves.
